Source: https://github.com/recharts/recharts/blob/main/storybook/stories/Customise.mdx

Renders a bar chart with custom triangle-shaped bars instead of rectangles. Uses TriangleBar component as shape property and CustomizedAxisTick for rotated axis labels. Demonstrates advanced shape customization in Recharts.

