### Style Recharts Bar Chart Elements with React/TypeScript

Source: https://github.com/recharts/recharts/blob/main/storybook/stories/Customise.mdx

This example shows how to apply direct styling to individual Recharts elements like `XAxis`, `CartesianGrid`, and `Bar` within a `BarChart`. Properties like `stroke`, `strokeDasharray`, and `barSize` are used to modify their visual appearance.

```tsx
import { BarChart, Bar, XAxis, YAxis, Tooltip, CartesianGrid } from 'recharts';

const renderBarChart = (
  <BarChart width={600} height={300} data={data} margin={{ top: 5, right: 20, left: 10, bottom: 20 }}>
    <XAxis dataKey="name" stroke="#8884d8" />
    <YAxis />
    <Tooltip />
    <CartesianGrid stroke="#ccc" strokeDasharray="5 5" />
    <Bar dataKey="uv" fill="#8884d8" barSize={30} />
  </BarChart>
);
```

